data.description: Welcome to this stunningly updated home in Red Oak! With its beautiful iron door and ceramic wood look floors, this home invites you in with its open floor plan and welcoming ambiance. The double master setup, including an In-Law Suite with a private entrance, is a standout feature. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting granite countertops and modern upgrades. The family room is equally impressive, featuring a charming fireplace. The updated bathrooms add a touch of luxury, while the large covered porch and fenced backyard offer ample space for outdoor activities. With 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, a flex room, and a separate office with a half bathroom, this home has all the space a growing family needs. The new water softener and osmosis system add convenience and quality. Situated on over a half acre of land, the home also offers a 3 car pass-through garage and a finished two-story She shade or Man cave with electricity. Don't miss out on this beautiful gem. Schedule showing a today!
